text: @UPSHelp Package I shipped Friday, but wasn't picked up until Monday because your driver decided to make our scheduled corporate pickup early (guess he wanted to start the weekend early), is now showing "Delay: Emergency Situation or Severe Weather". What's going on in NYC 10022?
